@dev Calculate the depth of the pool.
@param baseBalance The balance of the base token in the pool.
@param quoteBalance The balance of the quote token in the pool.
@param price The current price of the base token in terms of the quote token.
@return The depth of the pool.

@dev Decrease the price by a given increment.
@param price The current price.
@param increment The increment by which the price should be decreased (using full precision, e.g., 10 ** 18 = 100%).
@return decreasedPrice The new price after decreasing by the increment.

@dev Increase the price by a given increment.
@param price The current price.
@param increment The increment by which the price should be increased (using full precision, e.g., 10 ** 18 = 100%).
@return increasedPrice The new price after increasing by the increment.
